{"id": 933, "genre": 1001, "title": "你有什么使用大众点评的窍门？", "description": "排除水军影响，找到好吃餐馆——新时代技术工种。（题图来自：Franco Matticchio）", "record_count": 1880, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703130038y4iS0kjNqsUOLIoa.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-04-19T11:21:15Z", "options": [{"id": 69122, "content": "多吃！", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 532476}, {"id": 69123, "content": "必须要看带图的差评！", "image": null, "praise_count": 398, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 532353}, {"id": 69124, "content": "看餐厅和菜品图片，还有招牌菜", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 575352}, {"id": 69125, "content": "用美团", "image": null, "praise_count": 72, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 551051}, {"id": 69126, "content": "确定这不是给大众点评做广告？", "image": null, "praise_count": 196, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 477977}, {"id": 69127, "content": "说点啥呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 566207}, {"id": 69384, "content": "广告费多少？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 571537}, {"id": 69129, "content": "好奇心上的文章不错，更新频率小，但不能转载，希望更新频率高点。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 566207}, {"id": 69130, "content": "只根据大众点评搜索饭店跟图片，好不好吃我说了算", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 239090}, {"id": 69387, "content": "要是点评网站就避免广告嫌疑了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 380283}, {"id": 69132, "content": "点评上强烈推荐的菜，一定不要点！都是餐厅老板为赚钱的现金牛", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 69134, "content": "第一时间回复好奇心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 572573}, {"id": 69136, "content": "好评只说好吃 脆 甜甜的这种不靠谱形容词的一律pass。照片再美也没用", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 431002}, {"id": 69139, "content": "不如说说怎么看淘宝买家的评论", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 563393}, {"id": 69146, "content": "看的时候一般跳过前3个，因为那些大多数都是推广的", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 345973}, {"id": 69147, "content": "不看星级，而要看评论数量。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145587}, {"id": 69403, "content": "你让百度糯米情何以堪", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166753}, {"id": 69148, "content": "再看看美团百度糯米的评价", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 575031}, {"id": 69149, "content": "并没有，但凡差评都不会去", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 485695}, {"id": 69405, "content": "找差评", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 454604}, {"id": 69406, "content": "不用！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 577450}, {"id": 69152, "content": "我是来找窍门的", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182554Aa6bPLsNhiqVCwRS.jpg", "praise_count": 439, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274056}, {"id": 69409, "content": "高赞的 特别长的 置顶的评论看看图就行 不要盲目相信推荐菜 评价特别高或者特别低的点开那个人的全部评论看看是不是职业好评（差评）师 女生相信自己的第六感 看着真喜欢的就去试试吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 576798}, {"id": 70177, "content": "有钱任性。不需要窍门", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161642wXEcNmelAZrv7MfS.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 580265}, {"id": 69154, "content": "只想对评论说 拜托好看不等于好吃?️", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291951}, {"id": 69156, "content": "看人气美食和淘最上海啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 463733}, {"id": 69157, "content": "我就看看 不说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 107787}, {"id": 69158, "content": "现在的大众点评造假太严重了", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 397640}, {"id": 69159, "content": "我有使用美团的技巧，要么?(´･ω･`)", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 318532}, {"id": 69160, "content": "不要看星级评分，看带图评论，但忽略那些霸王餐评价", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 546350}, {"id": 69161, "content": "好奇心研究所也接广告了啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 296767}, {"id": 69162, "content": "好评一堆都是免费试吃反馈，不要去", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113515}, {"id": 69163, "content": "说，给力多少广告费?", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 563775}, {"id": 69164, "content": "当不清楚价钱不好意思进餐厅的时候，多看图，多学知识", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346986}, {"id": 69421, "content": "大众点评难道不是用来看地址和买优惠券的吗……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 50885}, {"id": 69166, "content": "点评是什么玩意？我从来不用 你觉得一帮大众能点评出来什么好东西。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 489058}, {"id": 69168, "content": "参考一下最新的评论！一般最新的都不是超级好评！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 504288}, {"id": 69680, "content": "对接朋友圈定位和菜单。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 576952}, {"id": 69171, "content": "不要看推荐菜，要看评论里的推荐菜！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 575540}, {"id": 69172, "content": "那种每句都用感叹号结尾的评论果断关闭。不具有参考价值。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113353}, {"id": 69173, "content": "不过主要是用来搜新餐厅的。仅作参考就可以了。人森经验还是靠自己垫的钱来补。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113353}, {"id": 69174, "content": "看网友评价", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 402216}, {"id": 69175, "content": "学习学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 563096}, {"id": 69176, "content": "看图", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 483895}, {"id": 69180, "content": "都不靠谱，只有靠自己的嘴", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 517443}, {"id": 69181, "content": "挑没有美图的照片看看品质，不要看卖家秀效果的菜拍照", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 575615}, {"id": 69182, "content": "只听朋友真实体验的反馈", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 493123}, {"id": 196671, "content": "没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1014942}, {"id": 69185, "content": "千万不要相信大家都说好的食物！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 573434}, {"id": 69186, "content": "只是搜索工具罢了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 481951}]}